      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> the horror Andaisin becomes the instant her mortal body dies — a Large undead <strong>Daughter of Urgathoa</strong>, Urgathoa's blessing on her most fervent. <strong>This is the true climax of Chapter 2.</strong> She fights to destruction, spreading plague with every claw.</p><p><strong>Tactics:</strong> wades in with reach claws + the pestilent aura, grabs and devours the wounded, and never relents. The fight begins fresh when she rises — give the party a beat of dread.</p>",
